    <entry>
      <title>MarkDown、Hexo、NexT 常用寫法</title>
      <link href="/2019/05/09/MarkDown%E3%80%81Hexo%E3%80%81NexT-%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E5%AF%AB%E6%B3%95/"/>
      <url>/2019/05/09/MarkDown%E3%80%81Hexo%E3%80%81NexT-%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E5%AF%AB%E6%B3%95/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<blockquote class="blockquote-center"><p>我不是一個偉大的程式設計師 我只是一個具有良好習慣的優秀程式設計師</p></blockquote><a id="more"></a><h2 id="MarkDown-常用寫法"><a href="#MarkDown-常用寫法" class="headerlink" title="MarkDown 常用寫法"></a>MarkDown 常用寫法</h2><hr><h3 id="字體基本設定"><a href="#字體基本設定" class="headerlink" title="字體基本設定"></a>字體基本設定</h3><blockquote><p>階層式區塊語法<br><code>&gt;text 、 &gt;&gt;text 、 &gt;&gt;&gt;text</code></p><blockquote><p><strong>粗體</strong>  <code>**your text**</code><br><em>斜體</em>    <code>*your text*</code><br><a href="https://jimmywei01.github.io/">超連結</a> <code>[超連結](https://jimmywei01.github.io/)</code></p></blockquote></blockquote><ul><li>小區塊<br><code>`your text`</code></li></ul><h3 id="標題"><a href="#標題" class="headerlink" title="標題"></a>標題</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># H1</span><br><span class="line">## H2</span><br><span class="line">### H3</span><br><span class="line">#### H4</span><br><span class="line">##### H5</span><br><span class="line">###### H6</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="文字增加顏色"><a href="#文字增加顏色" class="headerlink" title="文字增加顏色"></a>文字增加顏色</h3><font style="color:#f90;font-size:20px;">20px的字</font><br><font style="color:red;font-size:15px;">15px的字</font><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">font</span> <span class="attr">style</span>=<span class="string">"color:#f90;font-size:20px;"</span>&gt;</span>20px的字<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">font</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">font</span> <span class="attr">style</span>=<span class="string">"color:red;font-size:10px;"</span>&gt;</span>10px的字<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">font</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="表格"><a href="#表格" class="headerlink" title="表格"></a>表格</h3><p>冒號（Colons）是用來對齊的（擺左齊左、擺右齊右，都擺就置中）</p><table><thead><tr><th>Markdown</th><th style="text-align:center">Less</th><th style="text-align:right">Pretty</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><em>Still</em></td><td style="text-align:center"><code>renders</code></td><td style="text-align:right"><strong>nicely</strong></td></tr><tr><td>1</td><td style="text-align:center">2</td><td style="text-align:right">3</td></tr></tbody></table><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Markdown | Less | Pretty</span><br><span class="line">--- | :---: | ---:</span><br><span class="line">*Still* | `renders` | nicely</span><br><span class="line">1 | 2 | 3:</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="程式碼"><a href="#程式碼" class="headerlink" title="程式碼"></a>程式碼</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><figcaption><span>[language] [title] [url] [link text]</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">code snippet</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight plain"><figcaption><span>css test /index 首頁</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">  .container &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    max-width: 960px;</span><br><span class="line">    margin: 0 auto;</span><br><span class="line">    /* 起手式 */</span><br><span class="line">    margin-top: 10px;`</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><!-- <figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">```[language] [title] [url] [link-text]</span><br><span class="line">- [language] 是代碼語言的名稱，用來設置代碼塊顏色高亮，非必須；</span><br><span class="line">- [title] 是頂部左邊的說明，非必須；</span><br><span class="line">- [url] 是頂部右邊的超鏈接地址，非必須；</span><br><span class="line">- [link text] 如它的字面意思，超鏈接的名稱，非必須。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">``` css 阿阿</span><br><span class="line">  .container &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    max-width: 960px;</span><br><span class="line">    margin: 0 auto;</span><br><span class="line">    /* 起手式 */</span><br><span class="line">    margin-top: 10px;`</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>-->]]></content>
      
      
